
[[http://duttgroup-test.ics.uci.edu|DRG website testbed]] - you can try out new plugins and templates here without affecting the main webstie.


===== Access Control List =====
* If you set the global access permission of a group other than "ALL" group to be "None", the permission of the group would be the same as "ALL" group. 

===== File Sharing =====
1. Log in to drg machine (drg.ics.uci.edu) with your account \\
2. Execute the command "gsu duttgroup" which switches your account to duttgroup\\
2. Put your files into ~/public_html/papers/XXX\\
3. Then you can access it from **http://www.ics.uci.edu/~duttgroup/papers/XXX**\\
